<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN306-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai - atu; tuṟai - mūtiṉmullai. aḷḷūrnaṉmullaiyār. itu kaṇṭōr kūṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN306">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kaḷiṟuporak kalaṅku kaḻaṉmuḷ vēli</l>
<l>yarituṇ kūva laṅkuṭic cīṟū</l>
<l>rolimeṉ kūnta loṇṇuta larivai</l>
<l>naṭukaṟ kaitoḻutu paravu moṭiyātu</l>
<l>viruntetir peṟukatil yāṉē yeṉṉaiyu</l>
<l>mo<gap quantity="43" reason="lost" unit="character"/> vēntaṉoṭu</l>
<l>nāṭutaru viḻuppakai yeytuka veṉavē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>In the little village with pretty homes [and] a drinking well that is precious</l>
<l>that is stirred up when bull elephants fight [and] with a Kaḻal thorn fence,</l>
<l>a young woman with bright forehead [and] luxuriant soft tresses</l>
<l>without break worships an erected stone with [her] hands [and] prays:</l>
<l>“may I receive a guest”,</l>
<l>thinking “my lord …. together with the king</l>
<l>[and] the land-bringing excellent army will reach [here].”  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
